Description: Linux terminal monitor for CPU, memory and NVIDIA GPU metrics
 linmon is a small terminal monitor for Linux and WSL2.
 .
 It shows CPU, swap, memory and NVIDIA GPU metrics in an interactive TUI,
 and also supports JSON output for scripts and debugging.
